---
---

<section class="bg-white py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="animate-on-scroll text-orange font-bold text-sm tracking-widest mb-4" data-animation="fade-in">FLOW</p>
      <h2 class="animate-on-scroll text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-navy leading-tight" data-animation="fade-up">
        導入までの流れ
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative">
        <!-- Connection line (desktop) -->
        <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-16 left-[calc(16.67%+1rem)] right-[calc(16.67%+1rem)] h-0.5 bg-navy/10"></div>

        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="animate-on-scroll text-center" data-animation="fade-up" data-delay="0.1s">
          <div class="relative inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-navy text-white rounded-full mb-6">
            <span class="font-accent font-extrabold text-xl">1</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy text-lg mb-2">お問い合わせ・お申込み</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy leading-relaxed">
            Webフォームまたはお電話にてご連絡ください。
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="animate-on-scroll text-center" data-animation="fade-up" data-delay="0.3s">
          <div class="relative inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-navy text-white rounded-full mb-6">
            <span class="font-accent font-extrabold text-xl">2</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy text-lg mb-2">契約締結（年間契約）</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy leading-relaxed">
            電子対応にて年間契約を締結、お支払い開始。
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="animate-on-scroll text-center" data-animation="fade-up" data-delay="0.5s">
          <div class="relative inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-orange text-white rounded-full mb-6">
            <span class="font-accent font-extrabold text-xl">3</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy text-lg mb-2">サービス開始</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy leading-relaxed">
            ミライアカデミアへのアクセス &<br />
            初回コンサルティングの予約
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
